<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="h-100">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Uplead Forex Academy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }
      
      h2 {
        color: hsl(218, 41%, 15%);
      }

      h5 {
        color: #ad1fff;
      }

      /* Hero Section */
      .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-section img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .hero-text {
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .logout-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        right: 10px;
      }

      /* Services Cards */
      .card {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f0f8ff);
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px hsl(218, 81%, 75%);
      }

      /* Animations for Cards */
      .card {
        animation: slideInUp 0.7s ease-in-out;
      }

      @keyframes slideInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      /*Contact us*/
      #contact-us {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 50px 20px;
    }
    form {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    form button {
        background-color: hsl(218, 41%, 45%);
        border: none;
        color: white;
    }
    form button:hover {
        background-color: hsl(218, 41%, 35%);
    }
    

      /* Footer */
      footer p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #6c757d;
      }

      footer a {
        color: #ad1fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="container py-3">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#" style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Uplead Forex Academy</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                <button class="btn btn-dark logout-btn" type="submit">Logout</button>
              </form>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero-section">
        <img src="https://exc-prodp.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/uploads/what-is-forex-trading-and-how-does-it-work-og.png" alt="Uplead ForexAcademy Image">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Hi <%= name %>, Welcome to <span >Uplead Forex Academy</span> </h1>
          <p class="lead">Unlock your potential with expertly designed, profitable trading strategies that empower you to navigate the forex market with confidence. At Upleade Forex Academy, we provide you with the knowledge, tools, and mentorship to not only master trading but to achieve lasting financial freedom. Whether you're a beginner eager to learn or an experienced trader looking to refine your skills, our academy is your gateway to building a secure and prosperous future.</p>
          
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="learn-more" class="mt-5">
        <h2 style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>We are the leading forex trading academy, renowned for being trustworthy and reliable. At Upleade Forex Academy, we prioritize people's needs above everything else, ensuring tailored support for every learner. With over 500 students who have successfully transitioned into professional traders, we continue to empower individuals to achieve financial independence through expert guidance and structured learning.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="services" class="mt-5">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <!-- Section Heading -->
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p class="lead">Explore the wide range of services we offer to help you succeed in your trading journey.</p>
            
            <!-- Section Image -->
            <div class="my-4">
                <img src="https://blueberrymarkets.com/media/mjqhudpe/eurjpy-how-to-use-currency-strength-vs-weakness-in-forex-trading-blueberry-markets.png" alt="Services Image" class="img-fluid rounded">
            </div>
            
            <!-- Services Cards -->
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Forex Trading Course</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Master the fundamentals of forex trading, including the best technical and fundamental analysis using the price action model.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Mentorship</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Gain exclusive insights and personalized guidance to elevate your trading skills and achieve your goals.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Copy Trading with NeolinFx</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Don't have time to learn trading? Copy trades from me and enjoy the profits from my expert analysis.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 4 -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mt-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Trading Bots and Strategies</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Automate your trading with custom-built bots for MT5, with mobile versions coming soon.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
      <section id="contact-us" class="mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-center">We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us with any questions or inquiries.</p>
            <div class="my-4">
                <img src="https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/bltc23b87e0fef43b66/bltc78039f2c978fce7/6658888ce4a7320f3a978b82/Screenshot_2024-05-30_at_9.09.04_AM.png?format=pjpg&auto=webp&quality=90" alt="Services Image" class="img-fluid rounded">
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Contact Form -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <form action="/submit-contact" method="POST" class="p-4 shadow-lg rounded">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="message" class="form-label">Your Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Write your message here" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <!-- Contact Details -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4>Get in Touch</h4>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@upleadforexacademy.com</p>
                        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +123 456 7890</p>
                        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Avenue, Harare, Zimbabwe</p>
                        <h5>Follow Us:</h5>
                        <p>
                            <a href="#" class="me-2"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i> Facebook</a>
                            <a href="#" class="me-2"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i> Twitter</a>
                            <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    </main>

    <footer class="container text-center py-3">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Uplead Forex Academy. All rights reserved. Developed by <a href="http://www.elfo.co.zw" target="_blank">Elfo</a>.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
